  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Well, what do you think? Don't you want to get even more powerful than that? Pass a simple test and I'll do just that for you. Do you want to do it?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Good thinking. But, I need to make sure you are as strong as you look. It's not a hard test, one that should be easy for you to pass. First, take this letter...make sure you don't lose it."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Please get this letter to the #b#p424##k around #b#m10003080##k near #m10003000#. He's doing the job of an instructor in place of me. "
        },
        "2": {
          "_dirName": "2",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Give him the letter and he'll give you the test for me. If you want more details, hear it straight from him. I'll be wishing you good luck."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Really...it would help you a great deal on your journey if you get stronger fast. See me if you ever decide to change your mind. I'll make you much more powerful than you are right now."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Hmmm... it is definitely the letter from #b#p411##k ... so you came all the way here to take the test and make the 2nd job advancement as the thief."
      }
    }
